Comment: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:57.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,-------------------text-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:04.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,A書被女朋友找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.17,0:01:06.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,關鍵還是歐美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.84,0:01:07.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,香…香奈同學!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:10.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,今天是來考前複習的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.05,0:01:11.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,學個鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:14.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,反正千秋只會想這些事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:16.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,才 才沒有這樣的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:17.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 那麼想做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:18.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,做不就好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:25.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這 這種事情不是要再深一步的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:27.11,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是千秋你什麼也沒做不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:28.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,連接吻也還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:30.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這還不是因為你現在沒給人這種氛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:32.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,小伙子 怕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.16,0:01:34.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,吾 吾之名為千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.45,0:01:36.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,乃榮耀的恩恵之子與孝之子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:38.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那還不滾過來 不然把你頭轉下來!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:41.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那…那
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:50.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,香奈 意外的胸挺大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:52.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,超想揉 可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:53.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好勒 上了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:57.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦 接吻什麼還…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:01:58.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊不 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:00.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,剛剛的不算 不要在意!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.10,0:02:01.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不行不行不行 按順序 順序
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:04.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,大家在這種時候都怎麼弄得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:06.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是總先從接吻開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.11,0:02:08.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 我的嘴裡會不會臭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:10.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嘴唇也可能太乾燥了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:12.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說到底我一身汗真的不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:13.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,今天內褲穿的什麼樣式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:15.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 屁要是放出來了怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:17.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,乳頭的毛要是早點拔…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:18.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 大便
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:21.33,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,剛剛不是去過了嗎 你在逃避什麼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.33,0:02:23.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 不是的 想稍微準備一下什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:26.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,而且你對這種事情又不喜歡太急
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:29.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,「接吻了就是戀人了」這種話我也不想聽…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:35.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,香 香奈同學!? 女孩子不應該突然暴露裸體的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:36.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,囉嗦 笨蛋千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:38.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就算是我也不是只是著急想要接吻什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:41.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼說 只是想要變得更加在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:43.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以想要更了解千秋什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.52,0:02:45.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你也想要更了解我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:46.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,香奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.23,0:02:47.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,別看!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:47.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好狠!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:49.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,還說什麼想更了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:51.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,煩死了 色情千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:52.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,把燈關了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:56.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,話說在前面 我的身材並不是很好來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:59.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,還有今天沒時間洗澡所以汗什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:01.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是剛剛稍微看到了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.54,0:03:02.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,超美的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:06.33,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,笨蛋千秋 屎千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:05.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}明明在誇你 明明在誇你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:09.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是 我完全沒準備這種時候的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:12.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒 沒關係的啦這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:15.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,才不是沒關係啊 我去買回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:20.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是 今天出門的時候我媽說 要我拿著…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:23.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 也就是說已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:25.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喂 千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:27.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:28.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:30.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也喜歡你 香奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:34.86,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,吶千秋 快給香奈些點心…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:36.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是失敬了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:39.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,點心放這了 完事之後要吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:42.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,千秋他姐姐 不可以上二樓唷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:44.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:47.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒事 我家也像這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:48.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那繼續做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:51.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:55.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,有好好做避孕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:57.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我的借給你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:58.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,老媽!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:04.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,被學生會長看到抽菸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:05.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,還被表白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:08.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,而且作為條件居然還要我戒菸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:11.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:15.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,阿勒 我幹嘛老實戒菸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:20.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,話說不是沒說過要和我交往這種話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:23.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 梶同學 把我叫到這種地方有什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:26.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,赤木 我有話要跟你說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:28.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你不就是抓著我的弱點…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:30.33,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,弱點? 一被表揚就很害羞之類的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:34.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,才不是! 抽菸的事啊 而且你也沒說交往的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:36.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喔～ 那我再…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:36.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,別用你說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:38.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就接吻了一次就覺得自己是男朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:39.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,做了兩次喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:40.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,囉嗦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:43.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,又不是第一次接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:46.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這樣就想攻陷女生…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:48.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那你想要怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:52.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,都說了 為什麼對我…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:54.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,更愛一點? 真是拿你沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:55.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.82,0:04:57.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,來個鬼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:59.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說到底你根本沒喜歡我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:00.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒有這回事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:03.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,騙人 明明對我什麼都不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:06.66,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯 確實不是很了解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你看 果然是這…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:10.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,除了在學校看到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:12.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒有什麼朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:14.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上課時 也一直睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:18.59,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,明明可以早點回家卻在這抽菸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上次並不是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:25.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,之前就對你有興趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:28.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以你覺得表白了我就一定會答應嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:28.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:32.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我覺得梶同學 是那種只要被表白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:34.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就絕對不會拒絕的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:36.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你看 實際上就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:38.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以完全沒辦法放心把你交給輕浮的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:42.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嘛 作為我喜歡的人你肉還少了點就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:45.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,果然呢 說得好聽是個學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:47.33,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其實腦袋裡就只有些色色的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:50.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,確實如果能和梶同學一起睡的話我也想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:51.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:53.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那這樣的話現在就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:56.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以在你被其他男人搶走之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:58.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我要先霸占你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:06:00.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你從剛才開始都在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,都說了讓梶同學成為我的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:04.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真煩人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:08.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為你啊 像我這樣的傢伙 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:09.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,大概 因為喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:15.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,大概是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:16.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:18.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也沒有喜歡過別人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:21.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是如果這都不是戀愛那什麼是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:23.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我怎麼知道這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:24.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,試著弄明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:27.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,當然前提是你覺得沒問題的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:29.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不會勉強或是強迫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.67,0:06:35.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:38.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 要交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:42.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 那個 但是 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:43.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:45.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:49.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說「嗯」就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:50.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:57.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,之前我被皆川同學表白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:01.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是拖了好幾個月都沒有給她答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:08.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,到這時候再不答覆她的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:16.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,吶 古屋君 我已經等好久啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:18.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,差不多該告訴我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:20.59,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這 這個話題過下兩個人的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:21.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,Line怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:25.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那現在 我能收到結果嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:28.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,皆川你啊 到底是在玩還是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:29.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我判斷不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:32.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉 那我這次一定好好聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:33.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼說?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:35.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:37.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,交…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:38.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,交往不了吶?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:41.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我知道了 如果古屋君你沒有這個想法的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:44.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊不 那個 也不是沒有那個想法…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一提到要給答覆了… 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:50.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其實我才是不明白古屋君到底是在玩還是認真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:51.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那個 我不是這…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:52.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:53.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:56.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,馬上也要上課了 拜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:58.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦… 咦咦咦咦咦咦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:01.59,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒想到 居然這麼乾脆的放棄了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:02.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不對 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:03.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這其實也是皆川同學在演戲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其實在等我阻止她不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:09.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,傻嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:12.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,到底還是我不對啊 讓她等了那麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,總而言之過下再聊一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:16.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就算是皆川同學也多少會有些青澀的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:23.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不對啊這… 這不是放棄了而是心冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:26.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這也難怪啊 我這麼優柔寡斷的傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:29.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00A9A193\bord0\frz59.29\fs25\pos(633.333,288.667)}老盯著我幹嘛啊?(￢_￢)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:31.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦!? 為什麼會知道啊!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:33.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說起來 皆川同學不是在生氣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:35.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\c&H006B6C69\bord0\fs25\pos(585.333,282)\frz11.46}老盯著我幹嘛啊?(￢_￢)
