Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:37.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\c&H006B6C69\bord0\fs25\frz11.46\pos(834.666,215.333)}我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:37.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\c&H006B6C69\bord0\fs25\frz11.46\pos(633.333,411.334)}咦!?真的在看啊??（笑）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:39.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,開玩笑啦。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:41.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就是突然想調戲你一下。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:43.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,再者現在也沒有很急著想要答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:45.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:49.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\c&H006B6C69\bord0\fs25\frz345.3\pos(684,130.001)}咦!?真的在看啊??（笑）
