Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:15.86,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}熱を感じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:20.33,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}君といつだって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:25.62,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}同じ思い出ばかり
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:30.71,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}薄れてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:33.88,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}君の面影を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:38.39,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}見失うのが  怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:41.22,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}たった一瞬の
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:43.68,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}その景色を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.77,0:11:50.06,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}閉じ込めたくて  だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:55.49,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}あなたに出会えたことで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:12:02.03,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}強くいられたんだ ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:07.21,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}明日も目が覚めたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:13.09,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}すぐ隣にいる  と思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:19.18,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}ただそれだけでいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:09.02,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}回首仰望過去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:12.28,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}依然同那時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:15.86,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}感受著你的熱量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:20.33,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}無論何時同你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:25.62,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}全都是同樣的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:30.71,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}逐漸淡薄了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:33.88,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}你的面龐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:38.39,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}害怕這逐漸的  忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:41.22,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}只是一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:43.68,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}想把這份風景
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.77,0:11:50.06,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}鎖進我的心裡  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:55.49,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}想與你相見這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:12:02.03,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}卻很需要勇氣  一直如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:07.21,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}明明只是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:13.09,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}明天當我  睜開眼的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:19.18,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}你能在我身旁而已
